can outperform BERT in all\ncases, particularly the improvements are significant for Chinese. We also\ndevelop a method to improve the efficiency of AMBERT in inference, which still\nperforms better than BERT with the same computational cost as BERT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Aug 2020 00:23:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2020 05:29:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 06:53:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 27 May 2021 10:39:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-28"}
