c surface areas at the docking\nsite. Mutation of a small amount of residues can greatly reduce the hydrophobic\nbinding of the coronavirus to the receptor, which may be significant reduce\ninfectivity and transmissibility of the virus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Aug 2020 01:54:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-28"}
